<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Continuous_random_variable"=
>Continuous random variable</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=
=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/i=
ndex.php?title=3DStandard_deviation&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D7" titl=
