function">concave function</a>. The bias in the variance is easily correcte=
d, but the bias from the square root is more difficult to correct, and depe=
nds on the distribution in question.
</p><p>An unbiased estimator for the <i>variance</i> is given by applying <=
a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bessel%27s_correction" title=3D"Bes=
