\frac {1}{N-1}}\sum _{i=3D1}^{N}\left(x_{i}-{\bar {x}}\right)^{2}}}.}</anno=
tation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/df695c81f11c7d0d27209a42c72c20d2ad4e1fd2" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
