-align: -1.838ex; width:2.9ex; height:5.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle {\fra=
c {1}{N}}}"></span> and <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-in=
line"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"=
