ar {x}}^{2}}}\\[1ex]&amp;=3D{\sqrt {\left({\frac {1}{N}}\sum _{i=3D1}^{N}x_=
{i}^{2}\right)-\left({\frac {1}{N}}\sum _{i=3D1}^{N}x_{i}\right)^{2}}},\end=
{aligned}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
