l-align: -8.338ex; width:55.425ex; height:17.843ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle =
{\begin{aligned}{\sqrt {{\frac {1}{N}}\sum _{i=3D1}^{N}\left(x_{i}-{\bar {x=
