-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertica=
l-align: -0.338ex; width:6.511ex; height:2.009ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle r=
=3D{\bar {x}}.\,}"></span>
</p><p>Variability can also be measured by the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipe=
dia.org/wiki/Coefficient_of_variation" title=3D"Coefficient of variation">c=
oefficient of variation</a>, which is the ratio of the standard deviation t=
o the mean.  It is a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dimensionless=
_number" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Dimensionless number">dimensionless=
 number</a>.
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Standard_deviation_of_the_m=
ean">Standard deviation of the mean</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><spa=
n class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.=
org/w/index.php?title=3DStandard_deviation&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D=
26" title=3D"Edit section: Standard deviation of the mean"><span>edit</span=
></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r=
1320445320"><div role=3D"note" class=3D"hatnote navigation-not-searchable">=
Main article: <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Standard_error_of_th=
e_mean" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Standard error of the mean">Standard=
 error of the mean</a></div>
<p>Often, we want some information about the precision of the mean we obtai=
ned. We can obtain this by determining the standard deviation of the sample=
d mean. Assuming statistical independence of the values in the sample, the =
<b>standard deviation of the mean</b> (<b>SDOM</b>) is related to the stand=
ard deviation of the distribution by:
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttex=
t=3D"{\displaystyle \sigma _{\text{mean}}=3D{\frac {1}{\sqrt {N}}}\sigma ,}=
">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <msub>
